<lb n="0018b16"/><head type="no">No. 1036 [cf. Nos. 1034, 1035,
<lb n="0018b17"/> 901(Fasc. 5)]</head>
<lb n="0018b18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0018007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>千轉大明陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0018b19"/>
<lb n="0018b20"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0018008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宋）＋西【明】，（西天…臣）二十字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】</note><note n="0018008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣）二十字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0018008"><lem>西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿
<lb n="0018b21"/>傳<note n="0018009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法大師臣＝教大師【明】</note><app n="0018009"><lem>法大師臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">教大師</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0018b22"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時世尊在忉利天中波利質多
<lb n="0018b23"/>羅樹下。爾時帝釋天主。及與一切天人軍眾。
<lb n="0018b24"/>前後圍繞來詣佛所。各各至誠合掌歸依。瞻
<lb n="0018b25"/>仰如來次第而住</p>
<lb n="0018b26"/><p>爾時帝釋天主前白佛言。世尊我有陀羅尼
<lb n="0018b27"/>名千轉大明。是陀羅尼於諸世間。為大饒益。
<lb n="0018b28"/>所有一切天龍夜叉餓鬼鳩槃茶等乃至人非
<lb n="0018b29"/>人等。聞此陀羅尼者。悉皆降伏於諸眾生。所
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1036.0018c" n="0018c"/>
<lb n="0018c01"/>有一切不饒益事悉皆除殄。惟願世尊大慈
<lb n="0018c02"/>大悲許我宣說。佛言天主善哉善哉。如汝所
<lb n="0018c03"/>說彼大千轉大明陀羅尼。能於世間作大饒
<lb n="0018c04"/>益。汝欲說者當隨汝意。爾時帝釋天主。即說
<lb n="0018c05"/>千轉大明陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0018c06"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引一</note>曩呬怛寫婆帝<note place="inline">引二</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;
<lb n="0018c07"/>&CB00418;<note place="inline">引三</note>三野體難野過&CB00418;<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0018c08"/><p>一切部多聞此所說。驚怖迷悶狂惑退散。寶
<lb n="0018c09"/>賢夜叉主及輪成就等現眾色像。使諸部多
<lb n="0018c10"/>諸鬼神等及彼遊方空行起屍瘧病諸惡鬼
<lb n="0018c11"/>等。乃至一切行毒根本邪法。惱害眾生不饒
<lb n="0018c12"/>益事。悉皆解脫</p>
<lb n="0018c13"/><p type="dharani">阿曩<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;帝<note place="inline">引一</note>烏播曩<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;帝<note place="inline">引二</note>盎&CB00344;商迦
<lb n="0018c14"/>哩<note place="inline">引三</note>儗哩<note place="inline">二合</note>恨拏<note place="inline">二合</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引四</note>
<lb n="0018c15"/>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>野曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>達哩摩<note place="inline">二合引</note>野曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0018c16"/>僧伽<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">五</note>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路枳帝<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0018c17"/>濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">六</note>&CB00155;地<note place="inline">引</note>薩埵<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">七</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>薩
<lb n="0018c18"/>埵<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">八</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>嚕尼迦<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">九</note>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0018c19"/>哩野<note place="inline">二合</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>薩瑳<note place="inline">二合引</note>摩波囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00425;多<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0018c20"/>野<note place="inline">十</note>怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引十一</note>目訖帝<note place="inline">二合引</note>尾目訖帝<note place="inline">二合
<lb n="0018c21"/>引十二</note>鼻<note place="inline">引</note>那&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>尾鼻<note place="inline">引</note>那&CB00135;<note place="inline">引十三</note>&CB00135;哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>隸
<lb n="0018c22"/><note place="inline">引十四</note>尾摩隸<note place="inline">引十五</note>穌目契<note place="inline">引</note>尾目契<note place="inline">引十六</note>瞢&CB00344;隸
<lb n="0018c23"/><note place="inline">引</note>穌瞢&CB00344;&CB00619;<note n="0018010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十七〕－【元】</note><app n="0018010"><lem><note place="inline">十七</note></lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0018c24"/><p>一切王怖解脫。一切星曜變怪怖解脫。一切
<lb n="0018c25"/>自他軍眾<note n="0018011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00508;＝闡【宋】</note><app n="0018011"><lem>&CB00508;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">闡</rdg></app>戰怖解脫。一切兵仗怖解脫。一
<lb n="0018c26"/>切水火漂焚怖解脫。一切惡病苦惱怖解脫。
<lb n="0018c27"/>一切毒惡傷害怖解脫。師子怖象怖。熊怖虎
<lb n="0018c28"/>怖。一切惡獸等怖。大海漂溺怖深山&CB02880;寂怖。
<lb n="0018c29"/>乃至諸水灘難怖。如是諸怖悉皆解脫</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1036.0019a" n="0019a"/>
<lb n="0019a01"/><p type="dharani">曩謨娑<note place="inline">引</note>訖哩<note place="inline">二合引一</note>商迦致<note place="inline">引</note>商迦致<note place="inline">引二</note>迦嚕
<lb n="0019a02"/><note place="inline">引</note>致<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note n="0019001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＋（引）細註【明】</note><app n="0019001"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">嚕<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>致<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0019a03"/><p>入王宮時見大臣。時行軍中時逢怨對。時見
<lb n="0019a04"/>毒蛇毒龍。時遇夜叉毘舍遮羅剎烏&CB00425;娑摩
<lb n="0019a05"/><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0019002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【三】</note><note n="0019002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0019002"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>所魅時。乃至山海險難中時。如是怖
<lb n="0019a06"/>畏悉皆解脫</p>
<lb n="0019a07"/><p type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00718;婆&CB00085;室羅<note place="inline">二合引</note>野&CB00718;<note place="inline">一</note>呬&CB00619;
<lb n="0019a08"/>呬&CB00619;<note place="inline">二</note>唧&CB00619;唧&CB00619;<note place="inline">三</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>播&CB00619;<note place="inline">四</note>摩<note place="inline">引</note>鄧霓娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0019a09"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0019a10"/><p>又復王法所執或被枷鎖杻械牢固其身。一
<lb n="0019a11"/>切枉橫憂苦逼切悉皆解脫</p>
<lb n="0019a12"/><p type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>多<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>多<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引一</note>烏哆<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引二</note>&CB00418;哩
<lb n="0019a13"/><note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0019a14"/><p>又復星曜所持。或惡夢變怪致諸病苦夭枉
<lb n="0019a15"/>至死。乃至&CB00508;諍論理互相恐逼。如是諸怖悉
<lb n="0019a16"/>皆解脫</p>
<lb n="0019a17"/><p type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>左囉左囉<note place="inline">一</note>娑囉娑囉<note place="inline">二</note>尾娑囉尾娑
<lb n="0019a18"/>囉<note place="inline">三</note>沒馱野<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱野<note place="inline">二合四</note>&CB00155;<note place="inline">引</note>馱<note place="inline">引</note>野彌底
<lb n="0019a19"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">五</note>洛乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>洛乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">六</note>薩哩
<lb n="0019a20"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>薩<note n="0019003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛＝哩【明】</note><app n="0019003"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>喃<note place="inline">引</note>左娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引七</note>阿
<lb n="0019a21"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>滿哩馱<note place="inline">二合</note>覽<note place="inline">八</note>布瑟致<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0019a22"/>合</note>俱嚕娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0019004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（九）細註【三】</note><note n="0019004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＋（九）細註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0019004"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">引九</note></rdg></app>摩麼<note place="inline">引</note>布哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅滿
<lb n="0019a23"/>哩馱<note place="inline">二合</note>喃<note place="inline">十</note>扇<note place="inline">引</note>底孕<note place="inline">二合</note>俱囉娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十
<lb n="0019a24"/>一</note>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>賀帝<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;賀帝<note place="inline">引十二</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>努瑟
<lb n="0019a25"/>&CB01251;<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底孕<note place="inline">二合</note>惹&CB00135;<note place="inline">十三</note>謨<note place="inline">引</note>賀&CB00135;謨
<lb n="0019a26"/><note place="inline">引</note>乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>尼娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十四</note>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>迦致<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;
<lb n="0019a27"/>致迦吒致<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十五</note>曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>囉尼
<lb n="0019a28"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>囉尼<note place="inline">十六</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>囉尼娑
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1036.0019b" n="0019b"/>
<lb n="0019b01"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十七</note></p>
<lb n="0019b02"/><p>又復一切惡人行不善事。持邪禁&CB00057;作諸&CB01679;
<lb n="0019b03"/>禱。當令眾生迷癡狂惑。如是等事悉皆解脫</p>
<lb n="0019b04"/><p type="dharani">嚕嚕計<note place="inline">一</note>哩嚕計<note place="inline">二</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱夜<note place="inline">引</note>弭<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0019b05"/>夜&CB00085;&CB00344;&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>切<note place="inline">四</note>尾夢贊底<note place="inline">五</note>呬&CB00619;唧&CB00619;<note place="inline">六</note>迦
<lb n="0019b06"/><note place="inline">引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>隸<note place="inline">七</note>迦瑟站<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00344;薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>哆<note place="inline">八</note>薩哩
<lb n="0019b07"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆曳毘藥<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note></p>
<lb n="0019b08"/><p>世尊我此千轉大明。譬如轉輪聖王。有摩尼
<lb n="0019b09"/>寶名曰如意。凡諸所欲自然現前。我此千轉
<lb n="0019b10"/>大明亦復如是。若有得者凡諸苦惱悉皆解
<lb n="0019b11"/>脫。世尊末世之時眾生薄福。於三寶尊不知
<lb n="0019b12"/>歸依。恣身口心常造過惡。是故世間諸惡鬼
<lb n="0019b13"/>神伺得其便。隱自形質假託變現。於晝夜中
<lb n="0019b14"/>惱害眾生。使諸眾生得種種苦惱。世尊若有
<lb n="0019b15"/>眾生。遇斯惡鬼種種惱亂苦惱之時。乃至世
<lb n="0019b16"/>間一切不可意時。當於清淨之地取土七把。
<lb n="0019b17"/>每一<note n="0019005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">把讀＝一把【三】</note><note n="0019005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">把讀＝一把【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0019005"><lem>把讀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">一把</rdg></app>誦此大明加持七遍。和作七丸繫
<lb n="0019b18"/>於衣角。當令一切行不饒益惡鬼神等。不敢
<lb n="0019b19"/>侵近恐怖退散。當令是人晝夜安隱。一切不
<lb n="0019b20"/>祥悉皆殄滅。爾時帝釋天主說此千轉大明
<lb n="0019b21"/>陀羅尼已。踊躍歡喜與諸天眾禮佛而退</p>
